      </p>
      <p>
        The primary value of this platform is load analysis — understanding your connected load in kW, your daily and monthly energy consumption in kWh, and your electrical health. If you want a cost estimate, you can optionally provide your local rate. For offline use or sharing with an electrician, you can generate a professional <strong>electricity load calculator PDF report</strong> including your full appliance breakdown and, if a rate was provided, your energy cost estimate.
