      <p>
        Whether you are planning a new home, upgrading your wiring, sizing a solar system, or simply understanding your energy footprint, our <strong>electrical load calculator</strong> gives you the engineering-grade data you need. Add your appliances today for an instant load assessment, MCB and cable recommendations, an electrical health score, and smart energy-saving insights — no electricity tariff required.
